{"tid":2417873,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"CLS到底咩人會食冇花生醬既西多士","createTime":"2021-02-22T07:52:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T13:20:35.000Z","uid":357637,"like":23,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2a4c60f60c9f3b96b0f8ea2a446f71263471dec9","tid":2417873,"uid":357637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T07:52:47.000Z","msg":"西多士一定要有花生醬<br />\n根本就係靈魂<br />\n尤其是切九格 食中間嗰格 <strong>最 好 味</strong><br />\n唔明點解會有人唔鐘意食花生醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfee7d2a7e81a5827a0dd9f3361d694c18d77afc","tid":2417873,"uid":238920,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T08:09:45.000Z","msg":"都唔明點解有人食西多士<br />\n白麵包,花生醬,油炸,牛油,糖漿<br />\n所有野都係熱量炸彈<br />\n所以我十年都唔食一次西多士<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過食就一定要勁落牛油同糖漿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f709c788024a2ad26cf2c564f21ff9d34e3275","tid":2417873,"uid":330227,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T08:27:33.000Z","msg":"食大快活西多士嗰啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"267c502e2116e3a9004bedcfa2b6ca560a0bb908","tid":2417873,"uid":312578,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"99f709c788024a2ad26cf2c564f21ff9d34e3275","tid":2417873,"uid":330227,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T08:27:33.000Z","msg":"食大快活西多士嗰啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T12:50:26.000Z","msg":"食唔緊要，但係吹到好好食果d我真係指撚住佢個頭黎笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b0cb81a220be3c5396b4dcb79d65ff04cadf88","tid":2417873,"uid":330227,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"267c502e211